import React from 'react'
import {Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar from './Components/Navbar'
import Home from './Components/Home'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar />
      <Route>
        <Home />
      </Route>

      <Route>
        <About />
      </Route>

      <Route>
        <Contact />
      </Route>

      <Route>
        <Login />
      </Route>

      <Route>
        <Signup />
      </Route>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
